ime":"2017-11-01T09:32:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n 追返佢囉</blockquote><br />\n有追過<br />\n但佢好堅決咁拒絕我<br />\n明明相愛很難<br />\n點解會掉底我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n分左手好短時間?</blockquote><br />\n今日就岩岩一個月了<br />\n我係咪已經冇機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為咩原因呀?</blockquote><br />\n佢話我地淡左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你唔會傻豬啦<br />\n一定帽事</blockquote><br />\n搵人做過卧底<br />\n唔係帽事"},{"pid":"78e9f660ab2938c1373754b22519c9a12ab340da","tid":454440,"uid":19159,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T09:33:13.000Z","msg":"現任 佢係我最愛既一位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然當年我都好愛我ex 可惜佢唔愛我 得一個人堅持 冇咩意思 一齊左好多年 一個人撐唔到落去 到最後發覺 咁多年來唔分手只係因為唔甘心 而唔係因為仲中意<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時候會諗 如果可以早啲遇到現任就好 可以同佢經歷更加多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c057d0c7f1eb49293cf96653042b77d3f5c7ae43","tid":454440,"uid":116905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T09:39:09.000Z","msg":"現任<br />\n人生如戲 戲如人生<br />\n生命裡仿似等著現任的出現"},{"pid":"c05e1b8d0886075413a37e7a0a742c71521cf3df","tid":454440,"uid":144828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T09:44:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>現任 佢係我最愛既一位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然當年我都好愛我ex 可惜佢唔愛我 得一個人堅持 冇咩意思 一齊左好多年 一個人撐唔到落去 到最後發覺 咁多年來唔分手只係因為唔甘心 而唔係因為仲中意<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時候會諗 如果可以早啲遇到現任就好 可以同佢經歷更加多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor